title: Let's Play - Stainless Steel 6.4 - Medieval 2 Total War: Scotland #20 - A New Leader
description:
Part 20 of the Scottish Campaign.  A tragic death in the middle of a war campaign against Denmark.  Will a new leader take Scotland to glory or defeat?  Enjoy :D
